  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS OF BOLIVAR COUNTY, MISSISSIPPI, TO ESTABLISH A UTILITY DISTRICT WITHIN THE COMMUNITY OF CHOCTAW FOR THE PURPOSE OF OWNING, CONTROLLING, OPERATING AND MAINTAINING THE CHOCTAW SEWER ASSOCIATION SYSTEM FACILITIES; TO PROVIDE FOR THE POWERS AND DUTIES OF THE UTILITY DISTRICT; TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS OF BOLIVAR COUNTY TO TRANSFER ASSETS AND OTHER PROPERTY TO THE DISTRICT, AND TO CONTRIBUTE FUNDS AND SERVICES FOR THE REPAIR AND IMPROVEMENT OF THE SEWER SYSTEM FACILITIES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
